  "description": "A nighttime long-exposure photograph captures a vibrant cityscape bathed in the glow of city lights and fireworks. In the foreground is a long, illuminated bridge with symmetrical lighting and a modern cable-stayed design. Behind the bridge, the city skyline rises with numerous illuminated skyscrapers and buildings, creating a dense urban landscape. A burst of red, white, and blue fireworks explodes in the upper center of the frame, adding a celebratory element to the scene. The water below reflects the city lights, creating a shimmering effect. In the distant background, rolling hills and potentially other structures are visible, fading into the darkness.",
